                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.51/243.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-10-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 9, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The loan contract between American bankers and Nicaragua, of Sept. 1, 1911, was
                    approved today by the National Constituent I Assembly.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gunther.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
